        "text_7ttj7k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our goal at Satora Dreamer Cat is to ensure that our customers' experience shopping with us is great. Please contact our customer service for further assistance should you not be completely satisfied with your purchase online. Please make a return request <strong>within 60 days</strong> from the recorded date of delivery. Products returned outside of the stated period will not be accepted and returned to the original shipping address.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Quality-Related Return Process</strong></h3><p>To process your return request, we kindly ask for a valid Dreamer Satora order number and a brief explanation of the reason for the return to help us improve our service. Additionally, we request clear photos showing any product defects to support your return request.</p><p>Once your return is approved, our customer support team will provide you with the return shipping address. After we receive the item, our team will carefully inspect it to confirm the reported issue and ensure the product has not been damaged due to misuse. After the review, we will refund the full amount minus any shipping fees to your original payment method.</p><h3>How to Return Your Product</h3><p>Before returning your product, please ensure that the following:</p><ol><li>Place the product(s) back in the original shipping packaging to prepare for return. If the original packaging is unavailable or damaged, use a sturdy and protective replacement package that ensures the product is secure for shipping. Make sure the replacement packaging provides adequate protection to prevent damage during transit.</li><li>All products must be returned to us in perfect condition. Make sure all products are exactly as you received them.</li><li>Ensure that the packaging is securely fastened before shipping.</li></ol><p>Satora Dreamer Cat reserves the right to reject any returned products if the aforementioned requirements are not met or if the return request is only submitted after the 60 day time period after the receipt of the product.</p><p>Click the following button to initiate an exchange/return. Remember to include the following in the email:</p><ol><li>Order Number</li><li>Whether you want a return or exchange</li><li>The reason for return/exchanges</li></ol>"
          }
        },
