        "text_74bayF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>After your return/exchange has been processed, you are required to send the product (in the condition as described as below) using any carrier of your choosing. The return destination will be provided in a reply email from our support team after the return/exchange has been processed. <strong>Do note that you are required to bear the costs of the return shipping</strong>. </p><p>We will begin processing your refund/exchange after we have received and inspected the returned product(s). If we do not receive your returned shipment, we cannot proceed with the refund/exchange.</p><h3>Processing the Refund/Exchange</h3><p>Once we have received and inspected the returned product(s), we will send you an email to let you know if the request has been approved. If you are approved, then your refund/exchange will be processed. </p><p>If you applied for a refund, we will return the full amount of the purchase (minus any shipping fees) to the credit card that was originally used during purchase. </p><p>If you applied for an exchange, we will ship out the product of the same phone model in your exchange request. Once the product has been shipped out, we will send you a separate email informing you of the new tracking number for your shipment.</p><h3>Why have I not received my refund even though it has already been approved?</h3><p>Refunds usually take 3 to 5 business days to be credited back into your account as they need to be processed by various financial institutions. If your refund has yet to arrived after 5 business days, please get in touch with us.Â </p><h3>Damaged or Wrong Items</h3><p>Our apologies for the inconvenience. Please get in touch with us <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact Us\">here</a> within 7 days of receipt of the item and our support team will arrange a return for you if the product is deemed defective or if the wrong product was sent.</p>"
